\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf2 \cb3 What it actually is
\f1\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 OpenClaw is a fully autonomous AI agent that runs on your hardware, uses your API keys, and keeps your data private \'97 no subscriptions, no vendor lock-in. What makes it different from a simple chatbot: it doesn't just answer questions, it executes tasks on your machine including file management, code execution, and system administration. It has persistent memory, remembering context across conversations and building up knowledge about your projects and preferences.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://danubedata.ro/blog/self-host-openclaw-vps-ai-assistant-2026"}}{\fldrslt 
