\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
}}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 The key mental model is that OpenClaw sits between your messaging apps and your model configuration \'97 channels receive messages, and the Gateway routes each message to the correct session or agent. This decouples user interface from assistant logic, so you can keep your preferred communication apps while centralizing memory, tools, and automation in one place.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://enclaveai.app/blog/2026/02/14/openclaw-personal-ai-assistant-guide/"}}{\fldrslt 
