\f1\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 You don't open a browser or app. You chat naturally via WhatsApp, Telegram, Discord, Slack, Signal, iMessage, or even group conversations.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://medium.com/@gemQueenx/what-is-openclaw-open-source-ai-agent-in-2026-setup-features-8e020db20e5e"}}{\fldrslt 
