\f1\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 Real-world capabilities include web automation and browser control \'97 filling out forms, scraping data, navigating websites. Smart home control via Philips Hue, Elgato devices, and Home Assistant. Health data from wearables. Drafting and scheduling social posts. Managing email workflows through Gmail. Generating images, creating audio content. Over 565 community-built skills available.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.digitalocean.com/resources/articles/what-is-openclaw"}}{\fldrslt 
