\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf2 \cb3 Bottom line for your situation
\f1\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 Of everything discussed in this conversation, OpenClaw is probably the most exciting single piece \'97 a private, always-on assistant you can text from anywhere, running on your Mac mini, backed by either local Ollama or Claude depending on the task. The meal planning integration alone makes it worth exploring.\cb1 \
