\f2\b\fs27 \cf2 \cb3 One pattern worth highlighting\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 OpenClaw's Gateway architecture with its built-in cron scheduler, heartbeat system, and multi-channel delivery was built for the shift from "assistants into proactive workflow partners."\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://xcloud.host/proactive-openclaw-agent-workflows/"}}{\fldrslt 
