\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb7 Blink\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
}}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Roughly 1 in 5 plugins on ClawHub were malicious before a major cleanup in early 2026 \'97 and the registry is still not bulletproof.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.growexx.com/blog/top-10-popular-openclaw-skills/"}}{\fldrslt 
