\cf2 \cb3 8B models like Qwen3-8B, GLM-Z1-9B, and Meta-Llama-3.1-8B deliver enterprise-grade performance in resource-efficient packages.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.siliconflow.com/articles/en/best-open-source-LLMs-under-20B-parameters"}}{\fldrslt 
