\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
}}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0For your use case this tier handles: transaction categorization when descriptions are clear, simple natural language queries, basic email summarization, structured output (JSON for YNAB POSTs).\cb1 \
\cb3 Where 8B struggles: nuanced ambiguous cases, long-context reasoning, multi-step planning, subtle tone in written output.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf2 \cb3 14B \'97 the quality jump
\f1\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 The 14B model punches well above its weight, scoring 81.1 on MMLU \'97 territory that required 70B parameters just a year ago.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://awesomeagents.ai/leaderboards/home-gpu-llm-leaderboard/"}}{\fldrslt 
