\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb7 Awesome Agents\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
}}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0This is a meaningful inflection point. For your Amazon reconciliation, the 14B tier is the first model that reliably handles edge cases \'97 split orders across multiple shipments, unusual item combinations, context-dependent categorization.\cb1 \
\cb3 For iMessage-based daily interaction, the difference between 8B and 14B is the difference between "useful most of the time" and "I trust what it tells me."\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf2 \cb3 32B \'97 approaching frontier
\f1\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
