\f2\b 24GB M4 at $799
\f1\b0 \'a0is still the strongest value play. It runs Qwen 3 14B comfortably which is the sweet spot for all your listed use cases, and the ecosystem at 14B is improving fast enough that you won't outgrow it quickly.\cb1 \
\cb3 If retirement finance reasoning quality matters enough to you \'97 and there's an honest argument that it does \'97 the\'a0
