\f2\b\fs27 \cf2 \cb3 The iMessage reality check\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 iMessage is Apple-exclusive. It requires macOS to host a bridge. There is no supported way to send or receive iMessages from Linux, Windows, or any non-Apple hardware \'97 Apple actively blocks reverse-engineered bridges (Beeper Mini, pypush, and similar projects have been repeatedly shut down).\cb1 \
\cb3 So if iMessage integration is a hard requirement, your options are:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls53\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Wait for Mac mini availability
\f1\b0 \'a0\'97 they come back in stock, usually within weeks\cb1 \
\ls53\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Buy used/refurbished Mac
\f1\b0 \'a0\'97 Apple's refurbished store and Apple-authorized resellers often have stock when new Minis don't\cb1 \
\ls53\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Use a different messaging protocol
\f1\b0 \'a0\'97 give up iMessage and use Telegram, Signal, or WhatsApp instead\cb1 \
\ls53\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Run a hybrid
\f1\b0 \'a0\'97 non-Apple mini PC for the heavy LLM work, plus a small Apple device for iMessage bridging\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 Let me walk through each realistically.\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs27 \cf2 \cb3 Option 1 \'97 The "wait it out" approach\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 Mac mini stock cycles. M4 Mac mini availability tightened in early 2026 partly because of the OpenClaw phenomenon driving demand. Apple tends to restock within 4-8 weeks of a dry spell. If iMessage matters and you're not in a hurry, this is the path of least complication.\cb1 \
\cb3 Check these specifically: Apple.com refurbished store (often has M4 Minis at 10-15% off when new ones are sold out), Best Buy, B&H Photo, Costco, and authorized Apple resellers. Availability fluctuates daily.\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs27 \cf2 \cb3 Option 2 \'97 Used Apple hardware\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 A used Mac mini M2 Pro or M4, or a used Mac Studio M1/M2 Max, gets you back to the iMessage ecosystem. Some numbers:\cb1 \
